About this item

  • Unique Design of Pendant Lighting for Kitchen Island: mason jar light fixture is composed of a metal ceiling mount and the mason jar glass shade, add classy and elegant beauty to any interior with its modern farmhouse look. Perfect for living room bedroom, kitchen, porch or bathroom vanity and other places for decoration required.
  • Dimensions of this Farmhouse Light Fixture: Note: Please check the dimensions carefully before purchasing whether this pendant lighting fit your room.
  • Bulb Type of this Kitchen Light Fixtures: Requires E26 based bulb. Rated voltage: 110-240V. Compatible with all Incandescent, LED, CFL, halogen bulbs or other less than 60W bulbs with E26 Standard Base. Add an Edison style E26 bulb for a warm and inviting ambient glow.(Bulb NOT included). Kitchen lighting can be dimmable when you used with a dimmable bulb and compatible dimmer switch.
  • Quick & Easy Installation of this Dining Room Light: Includes all mounting hardware accessions and direction for quick and easy installation. Need to be hardwired. No on/off switch or plug in cord. In addition to following the user's manual, you need some patience and time to install these mason jar island lights perfectly. You will not regret it when you turn on the black ceiling light after installation.
  • After-sales service of this Mason Jar Chandelier: LMSOD is professional lighting manufacturer, We not only provide pendant light with guaranteed quality and reasonable prices, but also provide 2 years warranty and free replacement or refund within 30 days. if you have any issues or sugguestions, please contact us at first.

    Product Description

    • LMSOD 3 lights Kitchen Island Lighting is perfect for your daily lighting in the kitchen, living room, dining room, and cafe pub so on as well as a artistic decoration.
    • We have a series of such Island light fixture in our store now, including single sconce, double sconce, 3 lights sconce, 4 lights sconce etc.
    • Please keep an eye on LMSOD, more new arrivals will be launched soon.

    LMSOD 3-Light Adjustable Farmhouse Kitchen Island Pendant Light

    High-quality and mason jar shades make the light more bright and transparent. The great farmhouse look ensures it will be a perfect addition to your kitchen, dining room, hallway and stairway.

    Farmhouse Mason Jar Light Chandeliers

    Specifications:

    • Fixture Material: High-quality Metal and Mason Jar Pattern Glass
    • Color: Black
    • Finish: Painted
    • Number of Lights: 3 Lights
    • Adjustable Height: You can adjust the hanging height to reach your decoration request
    • Style: Design art living, original home fashion.
    • Easy Installation：Included all mounting hardware assembling accessories and user manual for quick and easy installation. You will not regret it when you turn on the industrial flush mount ceiling light after installation.

    Farmhouse Adjustable Mason Jar Chandelier

    Bulb Recommended:

    • Sockets: E26 Base
    • Voltage: 110-240V
    • Watts Wattage Per Bulb: Max 60 Watts
    • Bulb Type: LED/Halogen/Incandescent/CFL/Edison, recommend T45 shape bulb to fit the jars
    • Bulbs Included or Not: Bulbs are NOT included
    • Dimmable: It can be dimmable when you used with a dimmable buld and compatible dimmer switch to create the perfect atmosphere that makes you comfortable(Both NOT Included)

    We recommend installation by a licensed electrician.

    Please make sure you have cut off the electricity supply before installation.

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    Amazon Customer
    5 Stars
    It is truly a statement - Look what I did
    I purchased 2 sets, one of 5 Lights Linear Pendant and one of 3 Pendant light. I tried to use Anderson bulbs, but the 40 W were too bright for the eyes and 25 W were not bright enough for the kitchen. I got an elastic soft white wide band material from Joann Fabric - for $3. I made a tight "skirt" for each jar. The skirt blocks the brightness of the light bulbs (40W soft white), but soften the light, easy on the eyes. These lights created such a statement, it is modern, simple, vertical - make my kitchen looks bigger, interesting and inviting. But the Mansion jars are traditional, it is very blended with all the styles. I can take the "skirt" off to use Anderson Bulbs, which can be used when I have a party. Very happy with purchase.
